item.title: Season Review Part 1 of... Many
item.description:
panners and Trumpets are joined by Video editor extraordinaire Steve Amey and F1 Tik Tok titan Cristina Lee Mace as they take a backward glance to start the season reviews. From the Angsty Alfa Romeos, to the wondrous Williams to the, well, Ferrariest Ferrari, no silver lining goes without its cloud in this, the latest episode of Missed Apex Podcast.

item.title: Ep2: Lissandro & Viki Gabor
item.description:
It's the Junior Eurovision Song Contest final in Nice! Steve is joined by the reigning Junior champion Lissandro (and his mum). He won for France last year with Oh Maman! We're also talking to Viki Gabor, who helped Poland achieve back-to-back victories when she sang Superhero in 2019.


The Official Eurovision Song Contest podcast is produced and presented for the EBU by Steve Holden. The music is composed by Machine Sound. The artwork is designed by Chris Fox and Angela Espejo... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/6241e83524820b0012cb6bc7
